{"tid":2179963,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[樓市繼續gogogo] 盈翠半島2房撲千萬　貴樓上單位15萬","createTime":"2020-08-29T13:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:17:46.000Z","uid":339805,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6fb66b0d8a3350f6d8080e503f15e3bb741e4c","tid":2179963,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"疫情放緩，樓市回暖，有買家願高價購入優質戶。利嘉閣地產首席聯席市務董事彭錦添表示，青衣盈翠半島一個2房以近千萬元成交，有關單位為1座高層H室，屬實用518方呎2房戶，向東望荃灣西一帶海景，新近以990萬元易手，實呎19,112元。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，同座高5層H室，在今年7月底以975萬元沽出，即上述低層單位成交價較高層戶貴15萬元或1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2015年以766萬元購入，持貨5年，帳面獲利224萬元，物業升值29%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1598692897227&amp;issue=20200829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1598692897227%26issue%3D20200829&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=0c8a0d3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1598692897227&amp;issue=20200829</a>"},{"pid":"ee90f829c3daba3a3748cbe83e12854abfffb079","tid":2179963,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"租租點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db1815db7f3c8c6b245339088f2404bc1bfd960","tid":2179963,"uid":74094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}